  "detailed_description": "<strong>Step into the shoes of a private investigator drawn to an eerie family Manor, a sprawling estate shrouded in mystery and malevolence. Hired to uncover the truth behind a string of unexplained disappearances and disturbing phenomena, you must navigate the mansion's dark corridors, hidden passages, and ominous rooms. As you delve deeper, the line between reality and the supernatural blurs. Each clue unravels a piece of the manor's grim history, revealing restless spirits, malevolent entities, and ancient waygates.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/10fc0def3adab4b36863b350f9c969ba.poster.avif?t=1732908890\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/10fc0def3adab4b36863b350f9c969ba.webm?t=1732908890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/10fc0def3adab4b36863b350f9c969ba.mp4?t=1732908890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/076548b9c9fcb1994d94e9fa1d4ba223.poster.avif?t=1732908890\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/076548b9c9fcb1994d94e9fa1d4ba223.webm?t=1732908890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/076548b9c9fcb1994d94e9fa1d4ba223.mp4?t=1732908890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994970/extras/154